original: intros net nodes t e t' h l Hin. induction nodes as [|h' nodes' IH]. - simpl in Hin. contradiction. - simpl in Hin. apply in_app_iff in Hin. destruct Hin as [Hin | Hin]. + apply in_map_iff in Hin. destruct Hin as [(t'', l'') [Heq Hin']]. inversion Heq. subst. apply Hin'. + apply IH in Hin. apply Hin.
